OL,4,Cappointed Transport Secretary
OL,6,FHeidi Alexander has been appointed
OL,7,FTransport Secretary after the
OL,8,Fresignation of Louise Haigh over a
OL,9,Fundisclosed criminal conviction.
OL,11,FDowning Street announced the
OL,12,Fappointment on X on Friday 29
OL,13,FNovember. Heidi Alexander had been
OL,14,Fmade a justice minister after Labour
OL,15,Fwon the election in July.
OL,17,FMs Alexander said on X: "It's an
OL,18,Fincredible honour to have been asked
OL,19,Fto take on this role. Louise Haigh was
OL,20,Fformidable.
