OL,3,CSwindon South MP Heidi Alexander
OL,4,Cappointed Transport Secretary
OL,6,F"I will do all I can to ensure we have
OL,7,Fa transport system that drives
OL,8,Feconomic growth, connects our
OL,9,Fcommunities and protects the
OL,10,Fenvironment. A mammoth task ahead."
OL,12,FIt comes after Louise Haigh resigned
OL,13,Ffrom the role after it emerged she had
OL,14,Fincorrectly told police that a work
OL,15,Fmobile phone was stolen in 2013.
OL,17,FIn a letter to the Prime Minister, she
OL,18,Fsaid she is "totally committed to our
OL,19,Fpolitical project" but believes "it
OL,20,Fwill be best served by my supporting
OL,21,Fyou from outside Government".
