OL,6,FSky News and the Times newspaper
OL,7,Freported on Thursday 28 November that
OL,8,Fin 2014 she pleaded guilty to an
OL,9,Foffence after she was "mugged" the
OL,10,Fyear prior.
OL,12,FShe had initially reported to police
OL,13,Fthat her work phone device had been
OL,14,Fstolen, but claims she discovered
OL,15,F"some time later" that the device had
OL,16,Fnot been taken and that she had made a
OL,17,F"genuine mistake", from which she "did
OL,18,Fnot make any gain".
