OL,3,CSwindon South MP Heidi Alexander
OL,4,Cappointed Transport Secretary
OL,6,F"The original work device being
OL,7,Fswitched on triggered police attention
OL,8,Fand I was asked to come in for
OL,9,Fquestioning. My solicitor advised me
OL,10,Fnot to comment during that interview
OL,11,Fand I regret following that advice."
OL,13,FShe added: "I remain totally committed
OL,14,Fto our political project, but I now
OL,15,Fbelieve it will be best served by my
OL,16,Fsupporting you from outside
OL,17,FGovernment."
