OL,4,Cappointed Transport Secretary
OL,6,FIn a reply, the prime minister Keir
OL,7,FStarmer wrote: "Thank you for all you
OL,8,Fhave done to deliver this Government's
OL,9,Fambitious transport agenda.
OL,11,F"You have made huge strides to take
OL,12,Four rail system back into public
OL,13,Fownership through the creation of
OL,14,FGreat British Railways, investing
OL,15,F#1billion in our vital bus services
OL,16,Fand lowering cost for motorists.
OL,18,F"I know you still have a huge
OL,19,Fcontribution to make in the future."
